Summary: discovery of lunar anomaly and location
divs: sighting detailsfirst off i am an ex-air force tech - i take the subject of aerial phenomena pretty seriously. this is a little different...i recently discovered a site run by the us navy that holds the original clementine moon scan here's the link: *(link moved to additional evidence section--cms\sg). at this site at 19 degrees lat and 166 degrees long. are three enormous structures that we on earth didn't construct. they are huge...the 'castle' like structure measures 3 miles by 12 miles in size....you can even see these on googlemoon. anyone can see these!!!! please understand that there is a cover base on the far side of our own moon and nasa and the nsa probably knew. i have give this over the last two weeks to some politicians and news sources. the head of unsolved mysteries has them now and is working on a special about the subject. i do not feel that good about this discovery........our space research industry should have brought this to our attention...not me. judge for yourself
